{"tid":2193967,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部指印度軍隊先開火　促中印對話解決分歧  (中國唔敢還火)","createTime":"2020-09-08T08:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T08:35:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"65caeff463806b731d7dc432abe25e90477b8911","tid":2193967,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:28:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548492-20200908.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548492-20200908.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqC8TOYGSXSADKPC8%2B0d5FCk%3D&h=c9350d1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548492-20200908.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f9a6f25d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548492-20200908.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n印度反駁中國指印度軍隊非法越線的指控，反指解放軍鳴槍。<br />\n<br />\n印度軍方發表聲明，批評解放軍公然違反協議，進行侵略行動，儘管印中在軍事，外交和政治層面交涉仍在進行。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指，中國士兵試圖接近在拉達克地區的印度前線陣地，當遇到印度軍隊時，解放軍向空中鳴槍數次。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人趙立堅說，印度軍隊首先開槍，中方一再強調雙方通過和平，磋商，對話解決分歧，對抗對雙方都無好處，但他無資料中方有無開火。<br />\n<br />\n較早前，解放軍指責印度邊防軍，昨日非法越線進入中印邊境西段班公湖南岸神炮山地域，向前來交涉的中國邊防部隊巡邏人員鳴槍威脅，中國邊防部隊被迫採取應對措施穩控局勢。"},{"pid":"6f94767b5cbfadf0d46f2d3046bfd84f1c302927","tid":2193967,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ12vwXh.png&amp;h=785c542d&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"01cc6c66d5555674b03289d07a52a36facf87fbc","tid":2193967,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:29:59.000Z","msg":"立刻核平印度，中國是世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"412546632960527c63e81f62ed34cbcb0b596e4d","tid":2193967,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT